Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们又来到了裤头村滑浪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are again at the Bikini Bottom Boating School
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.30,0:01:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天又是海绵宝宝进行驾考的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today is once again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the day of SpongeBob's boating school exam
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but more importantly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.15,0:01:13.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是今年最后一次驾考
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is the last test for the year
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果海绵宝宝这次驾考又挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and if SpongeBob does not pass this one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.42,0:01:19.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就表示他又要再上一整年的驾校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:19.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it means another whole year of boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha' happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.97,0:01:26.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:26.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只是又撞上了个行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just struck another pedestrian
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再扣二十分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minus 20 more points
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还剩多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many does that leave me with?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,负224分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Negative 224
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我驾考还剩多少分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many more minutes left in the test?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经考完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The test is over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.42,0:01:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间还很充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扣的分还能补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can make up those points
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.82,0:01:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.18,0:01:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.72,0:01:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't hear me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.53,0:01:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mrs. Puff
