Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's my final score?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.81,0:01:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多少分才能过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And how many do I need to pass?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six
