Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, all you have to do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领到额外加分  过了我的课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to earn your extra credit and pass my class
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.75,0:03:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不用靠近这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and never have to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come anywhere near this school again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只要写句十个字的句子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is write a ten-word sentence
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主题是你在滑浪学校学到的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on what you've learned in boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我学了好多知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I've learned so many things
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便选一个  选哪个我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just pick one, I don't care which
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我替你开头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll help you get started
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在驾校里学了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What I learned in boating school is"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经七个字了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's already seven words
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要再写三个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only three more
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.47,0:03:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,L-E-A-R
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先削铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to sharpen my pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N-E
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你钢笔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a pen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钢笔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经典永流传的书写用具之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of the most permanent of all writing utensils
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gonna write an essay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I say
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.09,0:04:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我反悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I changed my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你写的什么都不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure whatever you've written it's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let me see
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't look
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.04,0:04:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not ready
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so simple
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要十个字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only ten words
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在驾校里学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What I learned in boating school is"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.00,0:04:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,填空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blankety
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,填空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,blankety
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,blank
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在驾校里学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What I learned in boating school is"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在驾校里学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What I learned in boating school is"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面感觉好热  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it hot in here, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么里面这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is it so hot in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hand
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的手抽筋了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hand is cramping, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只要再写
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You only need 
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more words
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.02,0:05:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看看你写的句子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let me see what you've written
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没写好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not ready yet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给老师看看你写的句子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show the teacher what you've written
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.06,0:05:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在驾校里学了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What I learned in boating school is"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剩下的都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the rest doesn't matter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You pass
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You pass
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我感觉我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, I don't feel like I really did anything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,额外加分本来就得这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how extra credit is supposed to feel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.13,0:05:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外这是你的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, here's your license
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,190)}裤头村驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1144,862)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My license
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宛如我梦中的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tastes just like I dreamt it would
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, I
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好人一生平安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice life
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心了  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个新司机要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a new driver on the road
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his name is
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈里斯  生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harris, happy birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破坏竟会如此之多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So much destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:36.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,472)}直播
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记者不禁要问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This reporter asks why
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地舆论一致认为问题出在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Local consensus places the blame
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位失职又自私的驾校教练身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on this negligent selfish driving instructor
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.05,0:06:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这段别播出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's not use that take
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's preposterous
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他都额外加分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He did the extra credit
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他连船都没得开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have a boat to drive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回家去  把面都吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to go home and have the rest of that pasta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:06.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,848)}感谢泡芙老师
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敬史上最棒的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the greatest teacher ever
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在此说出大家的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I speak for everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要把你当作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I say that we consider you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵家族的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a member of the SquarePants family
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该说的都说完了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you've made your point, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  本来我们还以为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, we were starting to think
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝绝对考不到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob was never going to get his license
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你从来没放弃过他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you never gave up on him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没打退堂鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never quit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没应付了事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never took the easy way out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只想让泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We wanted to make sure Mrs. Puff--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最好的驾校老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the greatest driving teacher in the world--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能来亲眼目睹这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was here to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目睹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,388)}我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,814)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I-M R-DY"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新汽船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A brand new boatmobile?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他明天就能开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be driving by tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toodle-oo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下大家都要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone will know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我放他毕业的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I let him slide through school
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须搬去另外的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to move to a new city
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外开所驾校  另外取个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,start a new boating school with a new name
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.28,0:08:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须把苗头遏制住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to end this thing before it begins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你摔得挺重的  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You took quite a buster there, son
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天在驾校里学了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I learned in boating school today is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是先放一放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to have to hold off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船的事情  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the driving there for a while, son
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  乖儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在床上躺好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, just stay in bed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要靠近船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no going near the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  小船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Boaty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小船  你着凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boaty, you're cold
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿我袜子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take my socks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小船  我会把你照顾好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Boaty, I'm always going to take care of you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是全海底最好的船了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the best boat in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我还记得怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope I still remember how to do this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在开船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm driving
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁  在我船上干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you and what are you doing in my boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么戴着滑雪面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you wearing that ski mask?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你压根就没滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because you're not skiing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.32,0:09:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  我知道你是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, I know who you are
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你根本就不认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know who I am
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认得可清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know that you're
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷船贼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a boatjacker
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然得用到这瓶胡椒喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd have to use this pepper spray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来人救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来人救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是为了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it was for your own good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把船还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back my boat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我停船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd better stop this boat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都阻止不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing will stop me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.05,0:10:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪怕有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1136,502)}巨蚌
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨蚌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giant clams?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不放手  哪怕有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting go even for
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese graters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1156,454)}奶酪擦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.07,0:10:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想让我放手  哪怕路上有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you think I'll let go for a little
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1072,540)}教育电视台
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教育电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Educational television?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来甩掉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like that got rid of him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放点音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for some tunes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到人渣电台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now back to KRUD
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来为你点播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with all of your personal
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你偷我车绝对要受制裁  金曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"You won't get away with stealing my car" hits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1122,148)}出事故请拨打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,754)}超级警察
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.11,0:11:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你偷到船的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd never let you have this boat
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算你是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even if you were
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你还好吗  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, how's it going, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,apologize
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不该让你过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have passed you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really weren't ready
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我得把驾照还回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, I guess I got to give my license back, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说比目鱼老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear Mrs. Flounder
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新开了一节周一早上的班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is starting a new class Monday morning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You kidding?
