Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides, the warden says she'll let you go early
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你帮人家忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you do her a favor
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么忙
