Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界一流水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool state-of-the-art jellyfish nets
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.13,0:12:27.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:27.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许摸
