Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母大电影里的水母叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The harpoon from Jellyfish: The Movie
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.22,0:12:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许摸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.27,0:12:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,僧帽博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dr. Manowar
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他被大兰尼蜇了都还能幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The guy who got stung by Big Lenny and lived
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个大包只有摸了才会疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now it only hurts when you touch it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非得我整天跟着你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I have to follow you all day?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是水母捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's The Jellyspotters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:59.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,186)}水母捕手
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村顶级水母迷俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's premiere jellyfish enthusiasts club
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有他们的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And their leader
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.35,0:13:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史上最酷的水母迷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the coolest jellyfish enthusiast ever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.27,0:13:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海参凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin the Sea Cucumber
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书呆海黄瓜有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so great about a nerdy pickle?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.52,0:13:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我能摸到他袖珍笔袋的褶边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I could just touch the hem of his pocket protector
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我大概就可以沾点他的光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then maybe some of his greatness would rub off on me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  身为你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, as a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得说那太书呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must say that's really geeky
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母杰弗里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jeffrey Jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走  杰弗里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Jeffrey
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要摸摸你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to touch you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竹子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bamboo?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我网柄只用复合材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only use composite materials in my net handle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,复合材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Composite materials
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next question
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next question
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.52,0:13:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is your question?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next question, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  废物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, loser
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  后边那位提问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you way in the back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有谁是真心想问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does anyone here have an actual
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your biggest fan
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真好心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're too kind
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Security
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.93,0:14:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都可以给你做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would do anything for you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你就跳楼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go jump off a building?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用拳头打自己脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Punch yourself in the face
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那样没伤着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that hurt you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我把自己伤着吗  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want it to hurt me, Kevin?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is the best
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家伙挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要带这位一起来捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have got to bring this guy jellyfishing with us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Kevin, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是怪才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a geek
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  我不会让他加入俱乐部的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, I won't let the guy join the club
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想看他要让水母蜇多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to see how many times he can get stung
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才会哭哭啼啼跑回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he goes running home like a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.55,0:14:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin's a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Genius
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想参加水母捕手的选拔测试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you like to try out for The Jellyspotters?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离床
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来水母田开敞篷兜风最舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like driving through jellyfish fields
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the top down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  水母捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eh, Jellyspotters?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敞篷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top down
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:23.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094,856)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.22,0:15:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你网没忘带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't forget our nets
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没忘带  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't forget them, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都在后备箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're in the trunk
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会跟水母捕手一起来这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm here with The Jellyspotters
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一生都想成为水母捕手的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean all my life I wanted to be a Jellyspotter
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在带着网和罐子跟你过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I'm here with you guys with the nets and the jars
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟凯文在一起  和大家聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm with Kevin and Kevin's with me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're all with each other
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起捉水母  超级有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're jellyfishing together and it's fun and
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在你加入水母捕手之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before you become a Jellyspotter
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须先通过严格的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to pass a rigorous test
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,严格的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rigorous test
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的第一项测试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your first test?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉一只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Catch a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我加入水母捕手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I a Jellyspotter now?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he caught one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.48,0:16:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加入俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the club
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只不算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that doesn't count
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说两只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant two jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进网了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the net
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说二十只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant 20 jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.40,0:16:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我数数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.86,0:16:38.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母捕手会让水母吃脸上的水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyspotters allow jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to eat jelly off their face
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想来舔我脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to lick my cheeks?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有水母来吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see I have some takers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tickles my nose
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not for long
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you cut that out?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在加入水母捕手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I in The Jellyspotters now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.94,0:17:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还有好几项测试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have many more tests for you to take
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在加入水母捕手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I in The Jellyspotters now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在加入水母捕手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I in The Jellyspotters now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
