Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.92,0:17:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.69,0:17:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.09,0:17:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
