Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.35,0:17:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在到你让水母电了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is your turn to get zapped
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好进行最后一项测试了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you ready for your final test?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd better be
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.15,0:17:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们要抓的是水母皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because we're going to capture a queen jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A queen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你  我们做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't do it without you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没当过诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never been bait before
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也没见过水母皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever seen a queen jellyfish either
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你大概就没用过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then you've probably never used
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母皇后哨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a queen jellyfish call
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先试试看好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前听过这种哨音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've heard this call before
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定听过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you have
