Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be right behind this bush
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁带了我的蜇伤药膏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's got my sting ointment?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我通过测试了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I pass this test
