Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should have seen the look on your face
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脸上的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when we zapped you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.08,0:19:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最后一项测试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what about my final test?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会真以为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you think
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.55,0:19:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们真会让你加入水母捕手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'd actually let youjoin The Jellyspotters?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was your biggest fan
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So were they
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin's back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin, please
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You looked so dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还吹笨得要死的水母哨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your dorky jellyfish call
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.92,0:20:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not a loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刺胞霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nideria rex
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母国王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King Jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲亲脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kissyface
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:38.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,322)}被蜇就用凯文药膏\N凯文的最爱
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它好像走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们哪位出去打探一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of you go out and check
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.25,0:21:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.42,0:21:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,save us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为了追赶潮流才加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just in this for the fashion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(570,364)}水母
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trapped
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trapped
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.43,0:21:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要小毯毯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my blanky
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要小毯毯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my blanky
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.20,0:21:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.36,0:21:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yummy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.75,0:22:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都爱吃派
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody loves pie
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  实在是太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, SquarePants, that was impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.50,0:22:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你还是不能加入俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you're still not in the club
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你没捉到水母皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you didn't catch a queen jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.97,0:22:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道这个原来是帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this was a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.12,0:22:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wasn't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.60,0:22:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.45,0:22:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.52,0:22:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你加入俱乐部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you get into that club?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来想  不过后来还是拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I turned them down
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.15,0:22:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是为凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not about Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.45,0:22:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是为了水母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.97,0:22:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  很高兴你学到教训了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I'm glad you learned your lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,崇拜偶像不健康
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hero worship is unhealthy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  杰弗里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Jeffrey
